    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Engage in intense battles with <strong>2 to 8 players</strong> in arenas full of surprises.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i> </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The goal</strong> is simple: be the last dummy standing! Use all the tools at your disposal to eliminate your opponents and <strong>stay alive.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i><u>Game parameter :</u></i></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Choose</strong> the number of <strong>lives</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Choose</strong> the number of <strong>HP per life</strong>.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Game modes :</u></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Classic </strong>choose your powers at the start of the match.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Random </strong>with each death, the power wheel spins.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Team</strong> choose either the orange or green team at the start of the match. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong><i>You can choose 3 powers from the available categories:</i></strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Movement</strong>: Choose powers like Super Speed or Super Jump to move faster or position yourself strategically.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ability</strong>: Select powers that modify your traits, such as Invincibility or Knife Throw, to dominate your enemies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Weapon</strong>: In addition to your pistol, choose secondary weapons like a Sniper or explosives to gain a tactical advantage. </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130430/extras/25c4bca8ac0ba9a002bb72b19bb318d1.avif?t=1772057399\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130430/extras_big/25c4bca8ac0ba9a002bb72b19bb318d1.webp?t=1772057399 width=1560 height=455 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong><u>9 maps are available right now. Come and discover insane arenas :</u></strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130430/extras/36bc52a80f560a41038185afcf98820b.avif?t=1772057399\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130430/extras_big/36bc52a80f560a41038185afcf98820b.webp?t=1772057399 width=1560 height=329 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i><strong>Unlock tons of accessories to customize your dummy!!!</strong></i></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130430/extras/5373c54cbc040422fbaab27009256f2f.avif?t=1772057399\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130430/extras_big/5373c54cbc040422fbaab27009256f2f.webp?t=1772057399 width=1560 height=200 /></span><strong></strong><br><br><br><br><br></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Earn boxes after every match</strong> and open them <strong>for free</strong> to unlock <strong>new accessories!</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>It’s up to you!</strong></u></p>",
